At TellusLabs, we are convinced that providing planet-wide coverage of our farms, forests, and water that is accurate, timely, and localized will change what's possible in tackling some of our toughest collective challenges. Insights fueled by spaceborne imagery are key to this vision. Yet today building meaningful signals from global-scale satellite imagery and other Earth data is harder than it should be.
